{
  "texts": [
    "His view reflects the practical challenges students faced in managing their time effectively within the designated window, leading to increased reliance on GenAI to handle the entire writing process.",
    "This finding echoes earlier research highlighting that time constraints, the disparity between the available time and the time needed to address a task (Benson & Beach, 1996; Rastegary & Landy, 1993), can impact students' decision-making and task operation behavior (Gonzalez, 2004).",
    "This study explored the expected role of GenAI in academic writing, including advantages and challenges, from students' perspectives.",
    "The findings suggest a range of implications for educational AI design and instructional strategies for AI-assisted learning to positively impact students' learning.",
    "First, students articulated the various roles they expected GenAI to serve during academic writing tasks, and acknowledged the benefits of GenAI-assisted writing."
  ]
}